trans-unit.source: Retrieval operations (including get) generally do not block, so may overlap with update operations (including put and remove). Retrievals reflect the results of the most recently completed update operations holding upon their onset. (More formally, an update operation for a given key bears a happens-before relation with any (non-null) retrieval for that key reporting the updated value.) For aggregate operations such as putAll and clear, concurrent retrievals may reflect insertion or removal of only some entries. Similarly, Iterators, Spliterators and Enumerations return elements reflecting the state of the hash table at some point at or since the creation of the iterator/enumeration. They do not throw ConcurrentModificationException. However, iterators are designed to be used by only one thread at a time. Bear in mind that the results of aggregate status methods including size, isEmpty, and containsValue are typically useful only when a map is not undergoing concurrent updates in other threads. Otherwise the results of these methods reflect transient states that may be adequate for monitoring or estimation purposes, but not for program control.
trans-unit.target: 检索操作（包括 get ）通常不会阻塞，因此可能与更新操作（包括 put 和 remove ）重叠。检索反映了自启动以来最新完成的更新操作的结果。 （更正式地说，给定键的更新操作与该键的任何（非空）检索报告更新后的值之间具有事前发生的关系。）对于聚合操作，例如 putAll 和 clear ，并发检索可能仅反映某些条目的插入或删除。类似地，迭代器，拆分器和枚举返回的元素反映了在创建迭代器/枚举时或此后某个时刻哈希表的状态。他们不抛出 ConcurrentModificationException 。但是，迭代器被设计为一次只能由一个线程使用。请记住，聚合状态方法的结果包括 size ， isEmpty 和 containsValue 通常仅在地图未在其他线程中进行并发更新时才有用。否则，这些方法的结果将反映可能足以用于监视或估计目的但不适用于程序控制的瞬态。

trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列代表的队列的头部。此方法与 poll 的不同之处仅在于，如果此双端队列为空，则它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of the queue represented by this deque. This method differs from poll only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列代表的队列的头部。此方法与 poll 的不同之处仅在于，如果此双端队列为空，则它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, if another thread is currently making an element available.
trans-unit.target: 如果当前有另一个线程正在提供一个元素,则检索并删除该队列的头部。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, or returns null if this queue has no elements with an expired delay.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此队列的头部，如果此队列没有延迟过期的元素，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, or returns null if this queue is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此队列的头部，如果此队列为空，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, waiting if necessary for another thread to insert it.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该队列的头部,必要时等待其他线程插入。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, waiting if necessary until an element becomes available.
trans-unit.target: 检索并移除该队列的头部,必要时等待,直到一个元素变得可用。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, waiting if necessary until an element with an expired delay is available on this queue, or the specified wait time expires.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该队列的头部,必要时等待,直到该队列上有过期延迟的元素,或者指定的等待时间到期。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, waiting if necessary until an element with an expired delay is available on this queue.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该队列的头部,必要时等待,直到该队列上有过期延迟的元素。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, waiting if necessary up to the specified wait time, for another thread to insert it.
trans-unit.target: 检索并移除该队列的头部,必要时在指定的等待时间内等待另一个线程插入。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue, waiting up to the specified wait time if necessary for an element to become available.
trans-unit.target: 检索并移除该队列的头部,如果需要等待到指定的等待时间,以使元素变得可用。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the head of this queue. This method differs from poll only in that it throws an exception if this queue is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此队列的头。此方法与 poll 的不同之处仅在于，如果此队列为空，它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last (highest) element, or returns null if this set is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除最后一个（最高）元素，如果此集合为空，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last element of this deque, or returns null if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列的最后一个元素，如果此双端队列为空，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last element of this deque, waiting if necessary until an element becomes available.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该deque的最后一个元素,必要时等待,直到有元素可用。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last element of this deque, waiting up to the specified wait time if necessary for an element to become available.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除该deque中的最后一个元素,如果需要等待一个元素可用,则需要等待指定的时间。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last element of this deque. This method differs from pollLast only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列的最后一个元素。此方法与 pollLast 的不同之处仅在于，如果此双端队列为空，则它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last element of this deque. This method differs from pollLast only in that it throws an exception if this deque is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此双端队列的最后一个元素。此方法与 pollLast 的不同之处仅在于，如果此双端队列为空，则它将引发异常。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the last element of this list, or returns null if this list is empty.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除此列表的最后一个元素，如果此列表为空，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the next watch key, or null if none are present.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除下一个监视键；如果不存在，则为 null 。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves and removes the next watch key, waiting if necessary up to the specified wait time if none are yet present.
trans-unit.target: 检索并删除下一个手表钥匙,如果没有钥匙,则需要等待到指定的等待时间。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves information (such as URLs) related to this referral. The program may examine or display this information to the user to determine whether to continue with the referral, or to determine additional information needs to be supplied in order to continue with the referral.
trans-unit.target: 检索与此推荐相关的信息(如URL)。程序可能会检查或向用户显示这些信息,以决定是否继续进行转介,或决定是否需要提供其他信息以继续进行转介。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves list of role infos (RoleInfo objects) of a given relation type.
trans-unit.target: 检索指定关系类型的角色信息列表(RoleInfo对象)。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves list of roles successfully accessed.
trans-unit.target: 检索成功访问的角色列表。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves list of roles unsuccessfully accessed.
trans-unit.target: 检索未成功访问的角色列表。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves names of all known relation types.
trans-unit.target: 检索所有已知关系类型的名称。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves notifications from the connector server. This method can block until there is at least one notification or until the specified timeout is reached. The method can also return at any time with zero notifications.
trans-unit.target: 从连接器服务器检索通知。本方法可以阻塞,直到至少有一个通知或达到指定的超时。该方法也可以在任何时候返回零通知。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves one of this Rdn's type. This is a convenience method for obtaining the type, when the RDN contains a single type and value mapping, which is the common RDN usage.
trans-unit.target: 检索这个Rdn的一个类型。当RDN包含单一类型和值映射时,这是获取类型的一种方便方法,这是RDN的常见用法。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves one of this Rdn's value. This is a convenience method for obtaining the value, when the RDN contains a single type and value mapping, which is the common RDN usage.
trans-unit.target: 检索这个Rdn的一个值。这是一种方便的获取值的方法,当RDN包含单一类型和值映射时,这是RDN的常见用法。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves one of this attribute's values.
trans-unit.target: 读取此属性的一个值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves one of this attribute's values. If the attribute has more than one value and is unordered, any one of the values is returned. If the attribute has more than one value and is ordered, the first value is returned.
trans-unit.target: 检索该属性的一个值。如果该属性有多个值,并且是无序的,则返回任意一个值。如果属性有多个值并且是有序的,则返回第一个值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves problem type.
trans-unit.target: 检索问题类型。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves role info for given role name of a given relation type.
trans-unit.target: 检索给定关系类型的角色名称的角色信息。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves role info for given role of a given relation type.
trans-unit.target: 检索指定关系类型的指定角色的角色信息。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves role name.
trans-unit.target: 检索角色名称。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves role value for given role name in given relation.
trans-unit.target: 检索给定关系中给定角色名的角色值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves role value for given role name.
trans-unit.target: 检索给定角色名称的角色值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves role value.
trans-unit.target: 检索角色值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves selected attributes associated with a named object. See DirContext.getAttributes(Name, String[]) for details.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象关联的所选属性。有关详细信息 DirContext.getAttributes(Name, String[]) 请参见DirContext.getAttributes（Name，String []）。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves selected attributes associated with a named object. See getAttributes(Name, String[]) for details.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象关联的所选属性。有关详细信息 getAttributes(Name, String[]) 请参见getAttributes（Name，String []）。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves selected attributes associated with a named object. See the class description regarding attribute models, attribute type names, and operational attributes.
trans-unit.target: 检索与命名对象相关联的选定属性。关于属性模型、属性类型名称和操作属性,请参见类的描述。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the "remaining new name" field of this exception, which is used when this exception is thrown during a rename() operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索该异常的 "剩余的新名称 "字段,当该异常在rename()操作期间被抛出时,使用该字段。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the Attributes view of the type/value mappings contained in this Rdn.
trans-unit.target: 检索此Rdn中包含的类型/值映射的“ Attributes 视图。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the EventContext that fired this event. This returns the same object as EventObject.getSource().
trans-unit.target: 检索 EventContext 此事件的EventContext。这将返回与 EventObject.getSource() 相同的对象。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the altName field of this exception. This is the name of the resolved object, relative to the context altNameCtx. It will be used during a subsequent call to the javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance method.
trans-unit.target: 检索此异常的 altName 字段。这是相对于上下文 altNameCtx 的已解析对象的名称。在后续调用 javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance 方法期间将使用它。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the altNameCtx field of this exception. This is the context relative to which altName is named. It will be used during a subsequent call to the javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance method.
trans-unit.target: 检索此异常的 altNameCtx 字段。这是相对于 altName 命名的上下文。在后续调用 javax.naming.spi.ObjectFactory.getObjectInstance 方法期间将使用它。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP control. The result is the raw BER bytes including the tag and length of the control's value. It does not include the controls OID or criticality. Null is returned if the value is absent.
trans-unit.target: 检索LDAP控件的ASN.1 BER编码值。结果是原始误码率字节,包括标签和控件值的长度。它不包括控件的OID或关键性。如果没有值,则返回空值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP extended operation request. Null is returned if the value is absent. The result is the raw BER bytes including the tag and length of the request value. It does not include the request OID. This method is called by the service provider to get the bits to put into the extended operation to be sent to the LDAP server.
trans-unit.target: 检索LDAP扩展操作请求的ASN.1 BER编码值。如果没有该值,则返回空值。结果是原始的BER字节,包括请求值的标签和长度,不包括请求OID。它不包括请求OID。这个方法被服务提供者调用,以获得要放到要发送给LDAP服务器的扩展操作中的位。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ASN.1 BER encoded value of the LDAP extended operation response. Null is returned if the value is absent from the response sent by the LDAP server. The result is the raw BER bytes including the tag and length of the response value. It does not include the response OID.
trans-unit.target: 检索LDAP扩展操作响应的ASN.1 BER编码值。如果LDAP服务器发送的响应中没有这个值,则返回空值。结果是原始的BER字节,包括标签和响应值的长度。它不包括响应OID。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ErrorManager for this Handler.
trans-unit.target: 检索该处理程序的ErrorManager。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the ID of the attribute that caused the sort to fail. Returns null if no ID was returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: 检索导致排序失败的属性的ID。如果服务器没有返回ID,则返回null。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the LDAP result code of the sort operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索排序操作的LDAP结果代码。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the MBeans associated to given one in a relation.
trans-unit.target: 检索关系中与给定关系相关联的MBeans。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the NamingException appropriate for the result code.
trans-unit.target: 检索适合结果代码的NamingException。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the Object to which resolution was successful.
trans-unit.target: 检索解析成功的对象。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the Reference of this object.
trans-unit.target: 检索此对象的Reference。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the StartTLS request's ASN.1 BER encoded value. Since the request has no defined value, null is always returned.
trans-unit.target: 读取StartTLS请求的ASN.1 BER编码值。由于请求没有定义值,所以总是返回null。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the StartTLS request's object identifier string.
trans-unit.target: 检索StartTLS请求的对象标识符字符串。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the StartTLS response's ASN.1 BER encoded value. Since the response has no defined value, null is always returned.
trans-unit.target: 读取StartTLS响应的ASN.1 BER编码值。由于响应没有定义值,所以总是返回null。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the StartTLS response's object identifier string.
trans-unit.target: 检索StartTLS响应的对象标识符字符串。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the address at index posn.
trans-unit.target: 读取index posn的地址。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the address type of this address.
trans-unit.target: 检索该地址的地址类型。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attribute ID of the sort key.
trans-unit.target: 检索排序键的属性ID。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attribute associated with this modification item.
trans-unit.target: 检索与该修改项相关联的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attribute value from the ordered list of attribute values. This method returns the value at the ix index of the list of attribute values. If the attribute values are unordered, this method returns the value that happens to be at that index.
trans-unit.target: 从属性值的有序列表中检索属性值。此方法返回属性值列表的 ix 索引处的值。如果属性值是无序的，则此方法返回恰好在该索引处的值。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attribute with the given attribute id from the attribute set.
trans-unit.target: 从属性集中检索给定属性id的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attribute's schema definition. An attribute's schema definition contains information such as whether the attribute is multivalued or single-valued, the matching rules to use when comparing the attribute's values. The information that you can retrieve from an attribute definition is directory-dependent.
trans-unit.target: 检索属性的模式定义。一个属性的模式定义包含了一些信息,如属性是多值还是单值,比较属性值时要使用的匹配规则。从属性定义中可以检索到的信息是依赖于目录的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attributes associated with an entry.
trans-unit.target: 检索与一个条目相关的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attributes in this search result.
trans-unit.target: 检索该搜索结果中的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attributes that will be returned as part of the search.
trans-unit.target: 检索将作为搜索的一部分返回的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the attributes to be bound.
trans-unit.target: 检索要绑定的属性。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the binding of the object after the change.
trans-unit.target: 检索对象变更后的绑定。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the binding of the object before the change.
trans-unit.target: 检索变更前对象的绑定。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the change information for this event. The value of the change information is service-specific. For example, it could be an ID that identifies the change in a change log on the server.
trans-unit.target: 检索该事件的变更信息。变更信息的值是与服务相关的。例如,它可以是一个ID,用于标识服务器上变更日志中的变更。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the charset that was detected by this decoder
trans-unit.target: 检索该解码器检测到的字符集。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the class name of the factory of the object to which this reference refers.
trans-unit.target: 检索该引用所指向的对象的工厂的类名。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the class name of the object bound to the name of this binding. If a reference or some other indirect information is bound, retrieves the class name of the eventual object that will be returned by Binding.getObject().
trans-unit.target: 检索绑定到此绑定名称的对象的类名称。如果绑定了引用或其他一些间接信息，则检索 Binding.getObject() 返回的最终对象的类名。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the class name of the object bound to the name of this binding. If the class name has been set explicitly, return it. Otherwise, if this binding contains a non-null object, that object's class name is used. Otherwise, null is returned.
trans-unit.target: 检索与该绑定名称绑定的对象的类名。如果类名已被明确设置,则返回它。否则,如果该绑定包含一个非空对象,则使用该对象的类名。否则,将返回null。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the class name of the object to which this reference refers.
trans-unit.target: 检索该引用所指向的对象的类名。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this composite name as an enumeration of strings. The effects of updates to this composite name on this enumeration is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的方式检索这个复合名称的组件。对这个复合名称的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this compound name as an enumeration of strings. The effects of updates to this compound name on this enumeration is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的形式检索这个复合名称的组件。对这个复合名称的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this name as an enumeration of strings. The effect of updates to this name on this enumeration is undefined. If the name has zero components, an empty (non-null) enumeration is returned. The order of the components returned by the enumeration is same as the order in which the components are numbered as described in the class description.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的形式检索此名称的组件。对这个名字的更新对这个枚举的影响是未定义的。如果这个名字的组件为零,则返回一个空的(非空)枚举。枚举返回的组件顺序与类描述中描述的组件编号顺序相同。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the components of this name as an enumeration of strings. The effect on the enumeration of updates to this name is undefined. If the name has zero components, an empty (non-null) enumeration is returned.
trans-unit.target: 以字符串枚举的方式检索这个名字的组件。对这个名字的更新枚举的影响是未定义的。如果这个名字的组件为零,则返回一个空的(非空)枚举。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the connection request controls in effect for this context. The controls are owned by the JNDI implementation and are immutable. Neither the array nor the controls may be modified by the caller.
trans-unit.target: 检索此上下文有效的连接请求控件。这些控件由JNDI实现拥有,并且是不可改变的。数组和控件都不能被调用者修改。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the contents of this URL connection.
trans-unit.target: 检索这个URL连接的内容。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the contents of this address as an Object. The result is a byte array. Changes to this array will affect this BinaryRefAddr's contents. Programs are recommended against changing this array's contents and to lock the buffer if they need to change it.
trans-unit.target: 以Object的形式检索该地址的内容。结果是一个字节数组。对这个数组的改变将影响这个BinaryRefAddr的内容。建议程序不要更改这个数组的内容,如果需要更改,请锁定缓冲区。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the contents of this address.
trans-unit.target: 检索该地址的内容。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the contents of this address. The result is a string.
trans-unit.target: 检索该地址的内容。结果是一个字符串。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties and no controls. The referral context is created using env as its environment properties and no controls.
trans-unit.target: 使用环境属性而不使用控件来检索继续该方法的上下文。引用上下文是使用 env 作为其环境属性而没有控件创建的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using environment properties. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索使用环境属性继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是间接遇到的,例如在搜索枚举中,引用异常都应该提供一个继续操作的上下文。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using request controls and environment properties. Regardless of whether a referral is encountered directly during a context operation, or indirectly, for example, during a search enumeration, the referral exception should provide a context at which to continue the operation. To continue the operation, the client program should re-invoke the method using the same arguments as the original invocation.
trans-unit.target: 使用请求控件和环境属性检索继续该方法的上下文。无论引用是在上下文操作中直接遇到的,还是在搜索枚举中间接遇到的,引用异常都应该提供一个可以继续操作的上下文。为了继续操作,客户端程序应该使用与原始调用相同的参数重新调用该方法。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method using the context's environment and no controls. The referral context is created using the environment properties of the context that threw the ReferralException and no controls.
trans-unit.target: 检索上下文，使用上下文环境在没有控件的情况下继续该方法。引用上下文是使用抛出 ReferralException 且没有控件的上下文的环境属性创建的。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the context at which to continue the method. trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if all of the following statements are true:
trans-unit.target: 返回 true 当且仅当下面的所有语句都是真实的：

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the argument is not null and is a Boolean object that represents the same boolean value as this object.
trans-unit.target: 当且仅当参数不为 null 且是一个表示与此对象相同的 boolean 值的 Boolean 对象时，返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the current thread holds the monitor lock on the specified object.
trans-unit.target: 当且仅当当前线程在指定对象上持有监视器锁时，才返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the designated bit is set. (Computes ((this & (1<<n)) != 0).)
trans-unit.target: 当且仅当设置了指定的位时，才返回 true 。（计算 ((this & (1<<n)) != 0) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the system property named by the argument exists and is equal to the string "true". (Beginning with version 1.0.2 of the JavaTM platform, the test of this string is case insensitive.) A system property is accessible through getProperty, a method defined by the System class.
trans-unit.target: 返回 true 当且仅当存在由参数命名的系统属性和等于字符串 "true" 。（从Java TM平台的1.0.2版开始，此字符串的测试不区分大小写。）系统属性可通过 getProperty 进行访问，该类是 System 类定义的方法。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the underlying class is a local class.
trans-unit.target: 当且仅当基础类是本地类时，才返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the underlying class is a member class.
trans-unit.target: 当且仅当基础类是成员类时，才返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if the underlying class is an anonymous class.

trans-unit.source: Returns true if and only if this CompositeData instance contains an item whose name is key. If key is a null or empty String, this method simply returns false.

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the argument is a finite floating-point value; returns false otherwise (for NaN and infinity arguments).
trans-unit.target: 如果参数为有限浮点值，则返回 true ;否则，返回false。否则返回 false （对于NaN和无穷大参数）。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the arguments are deeply equal to each other and false otherwise. Two null values are deeply equal. If both arguments are arrays, the algorithm in Arrays.deepEquals is used to determine equality. Otherwise, equality is determined by using the equals method of the first argument.

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the arguments are equal to each other and false otherwise. Consequently, if both arguments are null, true is returned and if exactly one argument is null, false is returned. Otherwise, equality is determined by using the equals method of the first argument.
trans-unit.target: 如果参数彼此相等，则返回 true ,否则返回 false 。因此，如果两个参数都为 null ，则返回 true ；如果正好一个参数为 null ，则返回 false 。否则，将使用第一个参数的 equals 方法确定相等性。

trans-unit.target: 返回 true 如果此描述的属性 OpenMBeanAttributeInfo 实例通过访问 isXXX 的getter（仅适用于 boolean 和 Boolean 值）， false 否则。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the attribute described by this OpenMBeanAttributeInfo instance is readable, false otherwise.

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the current compression type provides lossless compression. If a plug-in provides only one mandatory compression type, then this method may be called without calling setCompressionType first.
trans-unit.target: 如果当前压缩类型提供无损压缩，则返回 true 。如果插件仅提供一种强制压缩类型，则可以在不首先调用 setCompressionType 的情况下调用此方法。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the current input source has been marked as allowing metadata to be ignored by passing true as the ignoreMetadata argument to the setInput method.
trans-unit.target: 如果通过将 true 作为 ignoreMetadata 参数传递给 setInput 方法，将当前输入源标记为允许忽略元数据，则返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the current input source has been marked as seek forward only by passing true as the seekForwardOnly argument to the setInput method.
trans-unit.target: 如果仅通过将 true 作为 seekForwardOnly 参数传递给 setInput 方法，将当前输入源标记为正向搜索，则返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the current thread is a ForkJoinWorkerThread executing as a ForkJoinPool computation.
trans-unit.target: 返回 true 如果当前线程是一个 ForkJoinWorkerThread 执行作为ForkJoinPool计算。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the element (and the subtree below it) is allowed to appear in a metadata document for an image of the given type, defined by an ImageTypeSpecifier. For example, a metadata document format might contain an element that describes the primary colors of the image, which would not be allowed when writing a grayscale image.
trans-unit.target: 返回 true 如果元素（和它下面的子树）被允许出现一元数据文档中对于给定类型的图像，通过一个定义 ImageTypeSpecifier 。例如，元数据文档格式可能包含描述图像原色的元素，而在编写灰度图像时是不允许的。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the element is deprecated, false otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果该元素已弃用，则返回 true ，否则返回 false 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the format that this writer outputs preserves pixel data bit-accurately. The default implementation returns true.
trans-unit.target: 如果此编写器输出的格式准确地保留了像素数据，则返回 true 。默认实现返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the given Object is an ImageTypeSpecifier and has a SampleModel and ColorModel that are equal to those of this object.
trans-unit.target: 返回 true 如果给定 Object 是 ImageTypeSpecifier 并且具有 SampleModel 和 ColorModel 的是等于与此对象。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the given locale is supported by this locale service provider. The given locale may contain extensions that should be taken into account for the support determination.
trans-unit.target: 如果此语言环境服务提供商支持给定的 locale 则返回 true 。给定的 locale 可能包含在确定支持时应考虑的扩展名。

trans-unit.target: 如果给定图像具有与之关联的缩略图预览图像，则返回 true 。如果格式不支持缩略图（ readerSupportsThumbnails 返回 false ），则无论是否设置了输入源或 imageIndex 是否在范围内，都将返回 false 。

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the process of termination has commenced but not yet completed. This method may be useful for debugging. A return of true reported a sufficient period after shutdown may indicate that submitted tasks have ignored or suppressed interruption, or are waiting for I/O, causing this executor not to properly terminate. (See the advisory notes for class ForkJoinTask stating that tasks should not normally entail blocking operations. But if they do, they must abort them on interrupt.)
trans-unit.target: 如果终止过程已经开始但尚未完成，则返回 true 。此方法可能对调试有用。在关闭后足够长的时间内报告返回 true 可能表明所提交的任务已被忽略或抑制了中断，或者正在等待I / O，从而导致该执行程序无法正确终止。（请参阅类 ForkJoinTask 的咨询性说明，指出任务通常不应包含阻塞操作。但是，如果这样做，则必须在中断时中止它们。）

trans-unit.source: Returns true if the supplied source object appears to be of the format supported by this reader. Returning true from this method does not guarantee that reading will succeed, only that there appears to be a reasonable chance of success based on a brief inspection of the stream contents. If the source is an ImageInputStream, implementations will commonly check the first several bytes of the stream for a "magic number" associated with the format. Once actual reading has commenced, the reader may still indicate failure at any time prior to the completion of decoding.
trans-unit.target: 如果提供的源对象似乎是此阅读器支持的格式，则返回 true 。从此方法返回 true 不能保证读取将成功，仅基于对流内容的简短检查，似乎有合理的成功机会。如果源是 ImageInputStream ，则实现通常会在流的前几个字节中检查与格式关联的“幻数”。一旦开始实际阅读，阅读器仍可在解码完成之前的任何时间指示失败。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing the specified char. The result is a string of length 1 consisting solely of the specified char.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示指定 char 的 String 对象。结果是一个长度为1的字符串，仅由指定的 char 组成。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing the specified long. The argument is converted to signed decimal representation and returned as a string, exactly as if the argument and the radix 10 were given as arguments to the toString(long, int) method.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示指定 long 的 String 对象。该参数将转换为带符号的十进制表示形式，并作为字符串返回，就像该参数和基数10作为 toString(long, int) 方法的参数一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing the specified boolean. If the specified boolean is true, then the string "true" will be returned, otherwise the string "false" will be returned.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示指定布尔值的 String 对象。如果指定的布尔值为 true ，则将返回字符串 "true" ，否则将返回字符串 "false" 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing the specified integer. The argument is converted to signed decimal representation and returned as a string, exactly as if the argument and radix 10 were given as arguments to the toString(int, int) method.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示指定整数的 String 对象。该参数将转换为带符号的十进制表示形式，并以字符串形式返回，就像参数和基数10作为 toString(int, int) 方法的参数一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this Byte's value. The value is converted to signed decimal representation and returned as a string, exactly as if the byte value were given as an argument to the toString(byte) method.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此 Byte 值的 String 对象。该值将转换为带符号的十进制表示形式，并作为字符串返回，就像该 byte 值作为 toString(byte) 方法的参数给出一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this Character's value. The result is a string of length 1 whose sole component is the primitive char value represented by this Character object.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此 Character 值的 String 对象。结果是一个长度为1的字符串，其唯一组成部分是此 Character 对象表示的原始 char 值。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this Integer's value. The value is converted to signed decimal representation and returned as a string, exactly as if the integer value were given as an argument to the toString(int) method.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此 Integer 值的 String 对象。该值将转换为带符号的十进制表示形式，并作为字符串返回，就像将整数值作为 toString(int) 方法的参数给出一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this Long's value. The value is converted to signed decimal representation and returned as a string, exactly as if the long value were given as an argument to the toString(long) method.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此 Long 值的 String 对象。该值将转换为带符号的十进制表示形式，并以字符串形式返回，就像将 long 值作为 toString(long) 方法的参数给出一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this Short's value. The value is converted to signed decimal representation and returned as a string, exactly as if the short value were given as an argument to the toString(short) method.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此 Short 值的 String 对象。该值将转换为带符号的十进制表示形式，并以字符串形式返回，就像将 short 值作为 toString(short) 方法的参数给出一样。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this UUID.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此 UUID 的 String 对象。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String object representing this Boolean's value. If this object represents the value true, a string equal to "true" is returned. Otherwise, a string equal to "false" is returned.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此布尔值的 String 对象。如果此对象表示值 true ，则返回等于 "true" 的字符串。否则，返回等于 "false" 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String representation of this URL connection.
trans-unit.target: 返回此URL连接的 String 表示形式。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String representing a MIME parameter. Mime types may include parameters which are usually optional. The charset for text types is a commonly useful example. This convenience method will return the value of the specified parameter if one was specified in the mime type for this flavor.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示MIME参数的 String 。Mime类型可能包含通常是可选的参数。文本类型的字符集是一个常用的示例。如果在mime类型中为此风味指定了一个参数，则此便捷方法将返回指定参数的值。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String representing this Huffman table.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此霍夫曼表的 String 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a String representing this quantization table.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示此量化表的 String 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a ThreadInfo object represented by the given CompositeData. The given CompositeData must contain the following attributes unless otherwise specified below:
trans-unit.target: 返回由给定 CompositeData 表示的 ThreadInfo 对象。除非在下面另外指定，否则给定的 CompositeData 必须包含以下属性：

trans-unit.source: Returns a TrustManagerFactory object that acts as a factory for trust managers.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 TrustManagerFactory 对象，该对象充当信任管理器的工厂。

trans-unit.source: Returns a Type object representing the component type of this array. This method creates the component type of the array. See the declaration of ParameterizedType for the semantics of the creation process for parameterized types and see TypeVariable for the creation process for type variables.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 Type 对象，该对象表示此数组的组件类型。此方法创建数组的组件类型。有关参数化类型的创建过程的语义，请参见 ParameterizedType 的声明；有关类型变量的创建过程，请参阅 TypeVariable 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a Type object representing the type that this type is a member of. For example, if this type is O<T>.I<S>, return a representation of O<T>.
trans-unit.target: 返回表示该类型所属类型的 Type 对象。例如，如果此类型为 O<T>.I<S> ，则返回 O<T> 的表示形式。

trans-unit.source: Returns a Type object that identifies the parameterized type for the parameter represented by this Parameter object.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 Type 对象，该对象标识此 Parameter 对象表示的参数的参数化类型。

trans-unit.source: Returns a Type object that represents the declared type for the field represented by this Field object.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 Type 对象，该对象表示此 Field 对象表示的字段的声明的类型。

trans-unit.source: Returns a Type object that represents the formal return type of the method represented by this Method object.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 Type 对象，该对象表示此 Method 对象表示的方法的形式返回类型。

trans-unit.source: Returns a boolean indicating whether or not HTTP redirects (3xx) should be automatically followed.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 boolean 指示是否应自动遵循HTTP重定向（3xx）。

trans-unit.source: Returns a boolean indicating whether or not this StreamPrintService has been disposed. If this object has been disposed, will return true. Used by services and client applications to recognize streams to which no further data should be written.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 boolean 指示是否已 StreamPrintService 此StreamPrintService。如果此对象已被处置，将返回true。服务和客户端应用程序用来识别不需要写入更多数据的流。

trans-unit.source: Returns a double value with a positive sign, greater than or equal to 0.0 and less than 1.0. Returned values are chosen pseudorandomly with (approximately) uniform distribution from that range.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个带正号的 double 精度值，大于或等于 0.0 且小于 1.0 。从该范围（近似）均匀分布伪随机选择返回值。

trans-unit.source: Returns a float indicating an estimate of the number of bits of output data for each bit of input image data at the given quality level. The value will typically lie between 0 and 1, with smaller values indicating more compression. A special value of -1.0F is used to indicate that no estimate is available.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 float ，该浮点数表示在给定质量级别下对输入图像数据的每一位的输出数据位数的估计。该值通常在 0 到 1 之间，较小的值表示更多的压缩。特殊值 -1.0F 用于指示没有可用的估算值。

trans-unit.source: Returns a long value with at most a single one-bit, in the position of the highest-order ("leftmost") one-bit in the specified long value. Returns zero if the specified value has no one-bits in its two's complement binary representation, that is, if it is equal to zero.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 long 值与至多一个单个1位，在最上位的位置（“最左边的”）中所指定的一个位 long 的值。如果指定值的二进制补码二进制表示中没有一位，即返回零，则返回零。

trans-unit.source: Returns a long value with at most a single one-bit, in the position of the lowest-order ("rightmost") one-bit in the specified long value. Returns zero if the specified value has no one-bits in its two's complement binary representation, that is, if it is equal to zero.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 long 值与至多一个单个1位，在最低阶（“最右边的”）的位置在指定的一个位 long 的值。如果指定值的二进制补码二进制表示中没有一位，即返回零，则返回零。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigDecimal whose numerical value is equal to (this * 10n). The scale of the result is (this.scale() - n).
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigDecimal，其数值等于（ this * 10 n）。结果的小数 (this.scale() - n) 是（this.scale（）-n）。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose i-th bit corresponds to the i-th coefficient of the reduction polynomial for polynomial basis or null for normal basis.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger,对于多项式基础,其第i位对应于多项式的第i个系数,对于普通基础,返回空值。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (-this).
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值为 (-this) 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this % val).
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值为 (this % val) 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this & val). (This method returns a negative BigInteger if and only if this and val are both negative.)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this & val) 的BigInteger 。（仅当this和val均为负数时，此方法才返回负数BigInteger。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this & ~val). This method, which is equivalent to and(val.not()), is provided as a convenience for masking operations. (This method returns a negative BigInteger if and only if this is negative and val is positive.)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this & ~val) 的BigInteger 。此方法等效于 and(val.not()) ，是为了方便进行掩码操作。（仅当 this 值为负且 val 为正时，此方法才返回负的BigInteger 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this >> n). Sign extension is performed. The shift distance, n, may be negative, in which case this method performs a left shift. (Computes floor(this / 2n).)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this >> n) 的BigInteger 。进行符号扩展。移位距离 n 可以为负，在这种情况下，此方法执行左移。（计算 floor(this / 2n) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this << n). The shift distance, n, may be negative, in which case this method performs a right shift. (Computes floor(this * 2n).)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this << n) 的BigInteger 。移位距离 n 可以为负，在这种情况下，此方法执行右移。（计算 floor(this * 2n) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this * val).
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this * val) 的BigInteger 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this + val).
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this + val) 的BigInteger 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this - val).
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this - val) 的BigInteger 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this / val).
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this / val) 的BigInteger 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this ^ val). (This method returns a negative BigInteger if and only if exactly one of this and val are negative.)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this ^ val) 的BigInteger 。（仅当this和val中的一个恰好为负数时，此方法才返回负数BigInteger。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this mod m). This method differs from remainder in that it always returns a
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this mod m ）的BigInteger 。此方法与 remainder 方法的不同之处在于，它总是返回一个

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this | val). (This method returns a negative BigInteger if and only if either this or val is negative.)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this | val) 的BigInteger 。（仅当this或val为负数时，此方法返回负数BigInteger。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (this-1mod m).
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (this -1 mod m) 的BigInteger 。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (thisexponent mod m). (Unlike pow, this method permits negative exponents.)
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值为 (thisexponent mod m) 。（与 pow 不同，此方法允许使用负指数。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (thisexponent). Note that exponent is an integer rather than a BigInteger.
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (thisexponent) 的BigInteger 。请注意， exponent 是整数而不是BigInteger。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is (~this). (This method returns a negative value if and only if this BigInteger is non-negative.)
trans-unit.target: 返回其值为 (~this) 〜this）的BigInteger 。（仅当此BigInteger为非负值时，此方法才返回负值。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is equal to that of the specified long. This "static factory method" is provided in preference to a (long) constructor because it allows for reuse of frequently used BigIntegers.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值等于指定的 long 的值。此“静态工厂方法”优先于（ long ）构造函数提供，因为它允许重复使用经常使用的BigIntegers。

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is equivalent to this BigInteger with the designated bit cleared. (Computes (this & ~(1<<n)).)
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值等于该BigInteger，并且清除了指定的位。（计算 (this & ~(1<<n)) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is equivalent to this BigInteger with the designated bit flipped. (Computes (this ^ (1<<n)).)
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值等于该BigInteger的指定位被翻转。（计算 (this ^ (1<<n)) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is equivalent to this BigInteger with the designated bit set. (Computes (this | (1<<n)).)
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger，其值与此指定位设置的BigInteger等效。（计算 (this | (1<<n)) 。）

trans-unit.source: Returns a BigInteger whose value is the absolute value of this BigInteger.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个BigInteger,其值是这个BigInteger的绝对值。
